Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:05.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:08.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the miracle that happens \Nto a strong French black cat tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-There he is! Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:29.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We spotted Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Choppers one, two, and three!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:34.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After him! Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I serve up those three crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:56.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I heard you were Japan's \Nnumber one phantom thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but looks are so deceiving. \NI'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:01.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you wear that illogical, garish,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:09.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,old-fashioned outfit that \Nscreams, "Find me!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:13.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to imitate my country's \Nproud gentleman thief, Arsene Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-He's French?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Certainly, I'm impressed by how \Nyou stole that jeweled dagger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:23.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,from a heavily-fortified \Nart museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:27.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I could have done it \Neasily in half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then this guy's a thief, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chopper one, here! Chopper one, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We have visual confirmation of another \Nflying figure at one o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A flying figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:46.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's a black silhouette holding on\N to a paraglider next to Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! On the back of the paraglider...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A... a cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My name is Chat Noir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sunday at 9:00 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:03.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to our showdown \Nat Hotel Ocean at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}À bientôt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:53.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\a7}Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:53.01,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,11,,{\fad(1000,0)}Golden Eye (Part One):\NChat Noir's Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:56.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. What was that guy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:02.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, you said he identified \Nhimself as Chat Noir, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,Search
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:18.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Chat Noir" is French for "black cat," \Nand it's a famous phantom thief over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Black cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:26.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems he only targets cat's-eye stones \Nand ignores all other treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:30.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dressed all in black and \Nspecializing in cat's-eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hence, the Black Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then what about this \NHotel Ocean he mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a moment. I'll look into it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:47.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,French Black Cat Challenges \NKid the Phantom Thief!\NAt Hotel Ocean This Weekend...\NThe target is the "Golden Eye" \Nat the Marie Antoinette Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got some brass nads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:05:01.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Showdown Between Japanese \Nand French Phantom Thieves!\N\NKid the Phantom Thief versus Black Cat!\N Who will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"France's Phantom Thief, Chat Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,declares war on Kid the Phantom Thief\N with an advance notice."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:07.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"The target is the Golden Eye, which once \Ndecorated Marie Antoinette's index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will Kid take this challenge and show up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme my tablet back, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look, my dad's mentioned in the article, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:23.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"The other night, Inspector Takamori brilliantly \Nrecaptured the jewel-encrusted dagger,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,while Kid the Phantom Thief \Ngot away as fast as possible!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It says his approval ratings have fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:32.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's fine. It wasn't the \Njewel I was after, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if that cowardly Kid will show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It isn't the Big Jewel that I'm looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but when someone throws down the \Ngauntlet, I gotta pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, even if he does appear, \NI'm sure he'll get his butt kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're Japanese, \Nyou should be in Kid's corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! The police and my dad \Nare gonna be the winners!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've scheduled my \Nvacation at a different time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything depends on how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:27.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Since I'm here, I'll use \Nmy home-court advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:37.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,Marie Antoinette Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A glowing white line within the amber color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:59.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like a golden cat's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:03.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Golden Eye is a perfect name for this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan Mitsuishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:11.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Antoinette had seven talismanic \Naccessories to ward off evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:20.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That Chat Noir has stolen the \Nother six cat's-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:24.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's always right after a buyer is found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:31.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you should keep it locked up in \Nthe vault of your English mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to come all the way \Nto Japan and put it on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:41.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And at a hotel you built yourself\N in a remote area
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,between Tokyo and Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's all a trap to lure Chat Noir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. You capture Chat Noir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:55.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and you can take back the \Nsix cat's-eyes he stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the point of this whole exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:02.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We had a hand in this hotel \Nwhen it was constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:10.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Alain Cartier-kun, the head of a \Nsecurity company I summoned from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:18.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Especially since Japan's own thief\N is also after the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:22.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So what do you think about \Nconditions inside the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The security measures display an \Namateurish streak in many respects,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:31.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but at least there are plenty of guards, \Nso I don't think there will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So it was you, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:38.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreigner who found fault with \Nthe placement of my riot squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:43.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I don't trust anything \Nbut our own security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:49.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, Kid the Phantom Thief has made \Nfools out of you people for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There is no way I could trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:56.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch! Don't make \Nlight of the Japanese police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:09:00.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My people haven't let one \Nperson inside this hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I brought your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are these young people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:14.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My daughter, Aoko, and her classmate, \NKaito Kuroba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sloppy security on your part \Nfalls within my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unless the entrance to a rat cage is open,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the trap will catch nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Observe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:39.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...this thick, mounted window glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:45.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the titanium alloy wires can \Nwithstand ten tons of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, it isn't just in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:55.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Except guest rooms, all windows from the \N20th floor to the top floor here are that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:59.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the designated time, tonight at 9:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:04.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Five minutes before that, all elevators \Nwill stop and shut down at the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All stairs leading to the room\N will be blocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:12.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what this means,\N Monsieur Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Escape after 9:00 pm is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:20.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The paraglider and hang glider \Nthat Chat Noir and Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:25.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,are fond of making their escapes with\N will be utterly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:34.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why even the glass in the observation \Nelevator we rode up in had wires in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So it's easy to get in, but scary to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:43.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But all those wires ruined the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:49.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can replace that elevator \Nonce this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and you'll be able to see \Nthe magnificent view again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:11:01.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...if you keep that all-important ring \Nin this cheap glass case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, they won't be \Nable to steal it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you believe the \Nring should be protected by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the most reliable security \Nalarm device in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't see that here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:22.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Monsieur Nakamori, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You will be wearing Golden Eye on your finger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:31.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and waiting with it on top of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:36.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you keep a tight first until the \Ndeadline is over, it will not be stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:45.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll have you wear this gas mask \Nand a necktie pin fitted with a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They could try to steal it \Nafter putting you to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,or even take you into their custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a brilliant plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid will be shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He'd have to cut my finger off \Nto steal the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:10.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What if he does cut it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid would never be that barbaric...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:15.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...it's not beyond {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:25.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I mean Chat Noir, the phantom thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She's an investigator for an \NAmerican insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruby Jones-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Insurance company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:47.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. Mitsuishi-san made arrangements to \Nput out theft insurance on his jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so when she found out that Kid \Nis a master of disguise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She checked all of your faces too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Painstakingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:13:00.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the way we do things \Nin Texas, where I was raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:11.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is that the cat's-eyes have been \Ncleverly stolen every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so the company is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:17.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Suspicious that Mitsuishi-san \Nand Chat Noir are in cahoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:23.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If Golden Eye is stolen too, the \Ncompany will take a devastating hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So I was dispatched to \Nprotect it with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the job of the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:34.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't take Chat Noir seriously, \Nyou're in for serious trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:38.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a villain who has no qualms \Nabout hurting people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:45.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...what became of Mrs. Mitsuishi when she \Nwore a hair ornament with a cat's-eye inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:53.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chat Noir cut Mrs. Mitsuishi's hair \Nand absconded with the hair ornament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He didn't hold back, \Nbut hacked off hanks of hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:01.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My wife cried for one month \Nstraight after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:04.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Then he would hack off my finger...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:10.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we have you \Nput on a glove as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It will make you feel better, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bastard. It's not his finger \Non the chopping block...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:27.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this strategy even gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:31.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who called it \Na brilliant plan, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Annoying tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Suddenly springing this role on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This loop isn't attached to a shirt button,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so your tie is flopping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:59.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, Mitsuishi, Cartier, and Ruby...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:03.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All of them with frivolous, \Njewel-like names...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:08.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You took my name, Aoko, from the \N"blue" of a sapphire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:18.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like me, Ruby said her name was \Nchosen from her birthstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And she said our birthdays are close, \Nso we should be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:27.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But when we were talking about it,\N Cartier-san butted in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:33.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And he said, "Then was your \Nfriend born in December?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But you were born in June, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I asked Mitsuishi-san about it,\N he looked doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:46.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said, "Is the jewel 'chite' \Nany month's birthstone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I feel a little guilty for doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:05.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but a duel is a duel and a win's a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now I just have to set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From another country?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:26.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hi. Long time no see. Are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:30.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That sickly sweet and sarcastic tone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hakuba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've made the papers in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:39.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It says France's Chat Noir is \Ngoing up against you in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:44.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I ain't goin' up against anybody! It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:51.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you say so. I'll give you \Nthe info that I got from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:56.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chat Noir is a phantom thief who travels \Nthe world, only aiming for cat's-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:02.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Until three years ago, he threw away or \Nreturned the jewels that he stole, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm tellin' you, it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But ever since he started targeting \NDan Mitsuishi's cat's-eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,they've disappeared for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:15.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There were seven accessories, \Neach with an embedded cat's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:21.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan Mitsuishi's father was a Marie Antoinette\N fan, and they were part of his collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:25.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The accessories were sealed inside of a \Nvault for 30 years, but after the father died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan dug them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:33.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We don't know yet if they \Nwere really Marie's mementos,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:38.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but either way, those embedded \Ncat's-eyes are valuable jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and the designs are close \Nto items from that period,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:45.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so even historians tend to \Nthink that they're genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And speaking of design, I read \Na very interesting article.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The same thing seems to be happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I obtained past issues of this newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:03.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Several copies were sold the day\N after Chat Noir stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're really diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gathering information is one of the \Nfundamentals of being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So about this article,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:18.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,it says Chat Noir boldly left a \Nreplica of the accessory at the site
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:22.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,that looked exactly like the \NMarie accessory he stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:27.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The only thing different was that \Nit didn't contain the cat's-eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but looked like the jewel had \Nbeen taken out of the replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:36.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's about as far as I've gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:44.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now in Paris, it's 12:48:22.85.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In Japan, it's almost 9 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do your level best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to lose to anyone \Nuntil I catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. It's almost time \Nfor the Paris Collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:12.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez. I gotta envy any high school student \Nwho goes to Paris on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:23.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:28.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to see the \NParis Collection once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:45.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He told me to tell you he took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said to give this coin purse \Nto somebody named "Jii."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez. What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:20:00.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito's the one who suggested \Nwe bring Dad dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to lose this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, Monsieur Nakamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,thank you in advance for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Again, don't let them know \Nyou're wearing a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. They won't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have agreed to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:40.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What is this weird line of sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:17.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So, how are you going to attack, \NKid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:25.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm already set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A showdown between phantom \Nthieves of Japan and France.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:41.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, who will claim victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:49.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The illusion must go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.26,0:23:25.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master is busy with \Nhis showdown with Chat Noir,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so I'm handling the preview this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The strategy over the jewel heats up,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but which of them will laugh last?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:39.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NGolden Eye (Part Two): \NKid Versus Chat Noir: Endgame!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:39.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Golden Eye (Part Two):\NKid Versus Chat Noir: Endgame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way. Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:48.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a little confidence \Nin my English. Yes, I do.
